  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00001",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四云童、观音同上。〖点绛唇〗。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00002",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "观音"
      ],
      "text": "吾乃，白衣观世音是也。只因此地，有旱魃为虐，扰害黎民，不免遣土地前去，收服此怪。天灵灵，地灵灵，当方土地何在？",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00003",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "土地上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00004",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "我本一小仙，保佑地方安。忽听菩萨唤，急忙到跟前。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00005",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "菩萨见召，有何法谕？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00006",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "观音"
      ],
      "text": "今有王家庄，妖魔作乱，伤害黎民。命你前去，将他的宝贝打破，不得有误。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00007",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "领法谕。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00008",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "观音、四云童、土地同下。土地上。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00009",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "奉了菩萨之谕，前去降妖。待我变一固炉儿前去。一变，二变，固炉出现。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00010",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "土地换衣。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00011",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "无有担子，如何是好？不免将拐杖变来。急令勅。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00012",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "放火彩。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00013",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "担子已有，就此前往。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00014",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "有固炉儿出庙堂，挑起担子走四方。今日不上别处去，一心要上王家庄。王家庄有一个王员外，他家有三个好姑娘。大姑娘生来是个秃子，二姑娘头上溜油光。就算三姑娘头发好，当中无毛四面光。正走之间来得快，https://scripts.xikao.com/play/010160092021-12-10不觉到了王家庄。担子放在十字路口，㕭货声锯盘子锯碗，锯大缸。",
      "text_length": 174
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00015",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉锅哟！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00016",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王大娘上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00017",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "王大娘正在房中坐，忽听门外闹攘攘。用手开开门来看，只见固炉在街旁。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00018",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉锅哟！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00019",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "迈步出门开言道，叫声固炉儿听端详：昨日我打了个黄磁罐，今日又摔了一个腌菜缸。你若与我锯得好，快把价钱来商量。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00020",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉一听心欢喜，才出门来就要开张。不要你多来不要你少，铜钱只要你五百双。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00021",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "不给你多来不给你少，给你大钱一百双。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00022",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "你给一百双，是二百钱。好，就开开张。拿出来罢。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00023",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "拿什么呀？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00024",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "拿你的缸来呀。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00025",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "待我拿去。你看看罢。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00026",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "嗳唷，是一个破的呀！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00027",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你好混蛋呐！要是个整的，还叫你锯什么呀？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00028",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "这可是费锯子不少。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00029",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你看这个地方，锯上一道锯子。这块，再包上一个叶子。这儿，再钉上你妈那巴子。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00030",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "一道锯子，一个叶子，还钉上你妈那巴子。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00031",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你妈那巴子。你把担子挑进来，就在门里头做罢。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00032",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "好，我就这么办罢。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00033",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "我说你看什么呀？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00034",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "我常听人说，王家庄有一个王大娘，不知道在哪里住呀？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00035",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你问王大娘吓，不才就是我。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00036",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "怎么就是你能吗？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00037",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00038",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "人家都说王大娘，长得又丢丢，又勾勾。今个我这么一看，好比王胖子的裤腰带——稀松又平常。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00039",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你别见笑，今天是我起来太晚啦，头也靡有梳，脚也靡有裹，脸也靡有洗，衣裳也靡有换。你且在这里做你的活，我到后面梳洗梳洗，打扮打扮，叫你也开开左鼻子右眼睛。",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00040",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "好好，你去罢。我今天倒真要开开眼界。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00041",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "咱们回来见。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00042",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王大娘下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00043",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈，看她去打扮去啦，我不免做起活来。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00044",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉急忙把活做，想起当年事一桩。自幼生来命儿苦，不幸父母早双亡。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/010160092021-12-10留下我弟兄有三个，三人贸易俱经商。大哥开了个剃头铺，二哥修脚带开澡堂。惟有我的生意苦，每日挑担子在街坊。",
      "text_length": 133
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00045",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王大娘换衣暗上，坐。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00046",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉正在把活做，又听得高低响叮当。急忙回头来观看，大娘梳洗出绣房。走路好似风摆柳，扭扭捏捏赛过海棠。苏州香粉擦满面，朱红胭脂点在唇上。头上青丝挽螺髻，挑腮杏脸好风光。身穿一件绣花袄，八幅罗裙绣着鸳鸯。腰间紧系绫罗带，金莲只有三寸长。固炉越看越爱看，手里锤子着了忙。不觉一时失了手，走了锤子离了缸。",
      "text_length": 148
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00047",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你怎么不锯啦？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00048",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "破啦。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00049",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "呵，破啦。我也知道是破啦。你这个手艺是同你师妈学得吗？你给我说好听的罢！",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00050",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉这里开言道，尊声大娘听端详：大娘且慢别生气，我打破旧缸赔新缸。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00051",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "新缸靡有我旧缸好，哪有我旧缸腌菜香。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00052",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "固炉一见事不好，今天一定要闹饥荒。左思右想无主意，我挑起担子走他娘。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00053",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唢呐小调",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "叫声小子往哪里走，看你怎么对付老娘？我今与你拼了罢，担子翻在了大街旁。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00054",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "好啦，你这可赔我罢。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00055",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "我赔你什么呀？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00056",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "你看看，白花花，洒了一地金刚钻。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00057",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "一地是多少呀？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00058",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "一升零一把。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00059",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "你滚毬开罢！你要有他妈得那么些金刚钻，你也不当小炉匠啦！",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00060",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "text": "闲话少说，你看怎么办罢？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016009_e00061",
      "play_id": "01016009",
      "scene_id": "01016009_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王大娘"
      ],
      "text": "怎么办？今个你就走不了了。要叫你试试我的厉害。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
